text: Elimination Chamber (2015) (also known as No Escape (2015) in Germany) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on May 31, 2015 at American Bank Center in Corpus Christi, Texas. It was the sixth Elimination Chamber event held by WWE. 20,000 fans bought tickets for the event. The main event saw Dean Ambrose defeat WWE World Heavyweight Champion Seth Rollins by disqualification. This was also the first event to have a tag team Elimination Chamber match.
